data.description: Gorgeous home located in the Kingswood Heights Community within walking distance to downtown Grove City! This 4 Bedroom 2.5 Bath home has been updated & is ready to move in! The covered front porch welcomes you into this warm & cozy home. The Living Room is open to the Dining Area. In the Kitchen you will find stainless appliances, plenty of cabinetry & countertop space plus wood flooring! The Kitchen has a breakfast bar which opens to the Family Room! Upstairs are 4 roomy Bedrms! The Master Bedrm is spacious & has its own private bath. The additional room in lower level is being used as a 5th Bedrm. Outside is a full covered porch patio. Relax while enjoying the amazing firepit area on those chilly evenings. Under Documents there is a list of Updates & Improvements!  Hurry to see today!
